query:
SELECT 
  id,
  nome,
  dum,
  dataUltrassom,
  dataNascimento,
  createdAt,
  updatedAt,
  LENGTH(dum) as len_dum,
  LENGTH(dataUltrassom) as len_dataUS,
  LENGTH(dataNascimento) as len_dataNasc
FROM gestantes 
WHERE email = 'teste@gestantesapp.com'
LIMIT 1;
